item.title: Sales Mastery Unleashed: Insights from Jarrod Best-Mitchell
item.description:
The Entrepreneurial You: Episode 333 - Sales Mastery Unleashed: Insights from Jarrod Best-Mitchell
Over the past 17 years, my next guest has been successful in B2B & B2C sales for companies such as Digicel, DHL, Nokia, Microsoft, and Samsung. Since 2019, he has trained hundreds of sales professionals in the Insurance, Finance, FMCG, Real Estate, Media, and Telecoms industries.
